<taxonomicName id="4C354D64FFBE6271FD8A59C74011F802" authority="Chamisso &amp; Schlechtendal (1827: 570)" authorityName="Chamisso &amp; Schlechtendal" authorityPageNumber="570" authorityYear="1827" box="[561,1147,1995,2022]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Linderniaceae" genus="Lindernia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="232" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="crustacea">
